<div id="review_2227499378" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2227499378" />
    <a title="Leah" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4583211-leah"><img alt="Leah" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1588705957p2/4583211.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2227499378?book_show_action=true">Dec 26, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Leah" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Leah" href="/user/show/4583211-leah">Leah</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4583211-leah?shelf=kids-books">kids-books</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2227499378" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8998962683669601621">I randomly found this book for fifty cents at a library sale. I always get some new Christmas books for my children, a feisty daughter and her older brother. They get along like most siblings do, (about half the time!). I had no idea what this book was about, Just liked the price. Well, I should have read it to myself before reading it to them because the end had me choking up. The sweet message of sibling love is just so sweet. This is now one of my favorite children’s books! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


